query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 0 AND q.view_count <= 100
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('askubuntu')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('14.04',
'16.04',
'apt',
'boot',
'command-line',
'dual-boot',
'grub2',
'partitioning',
'server',
'system-installation');
